<h1>The Reading List</h1>

<p>No reviews. No ratings. Inspired by <a href="https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2017/05/keeping-track-of-every-book-youve-ever-read/526779/">Pamela Paul</a></p>

- bookCount = data.reading.books.count { |book| book.author.present?}

%table.table{style:"counter-reset:rowNumber #{bookCount+1}"}
  - data.reading.books.each do |book| 
    - if book.author.blank?
      %tr.htr
        %th{colspan: "3"}= book.title
    - else
      %tr
        %td . 
        %td= book.title
        %td= book.author

